2. Documentation, analysis notes, and diagrams
----------------------------------------------
Files: every Markdown file (`*.md`) in this repository, including all files
under `validation/architecture/`; every Mermaid diagram (`*.mmd`); every rendered
diagram (`*.png`) under `validation/findings/functions/`; the project `README.md`;
and the PDF reference material under `docs/` that is the author's original work.

