Notes on scope
--------------
- The `docs/ECU Firmware RE.pdf` file is licensed under CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 as
  part of the documentation set, to the extent it is the author's original
  work.
- Third-party material referenced by the lab (the Infineon TC1766 User Manual,
  the ISO 14229 UDS specification, the Ghidra decompiler output convention)
  remains under its own respective licence; no portion of any third-party
  document is redistributed in this repository.
- The Permitted Use section of `README.md` records the educational/research
  framing under which this lab is published. Nothing in this licence file is
  intended to displace that framing or to authorise use against systems the
  reader does not own.
